      <title>台积电获得美国 116 亿美元赠款和贷款用于芯片工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tsmc-gets-11-6-billion-in-us-grants-loans-for-three-chip-fabs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国计划向台积电提供 66 亿美元的赠款和高达 50 亿美元的贷款，帮助这家全球顶级芯片制造商在亚利桑那州建设工厂，扩大总统乔·拜登促进关键技术国内生产的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tsmc-gets-11-6-billion-in-us-grants-loans-for-three-chip-fabs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
